desktop-defaults (0.10.34) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Use #!/bin/sh shebang lines, not dash specific. Drop package dependency
    on dash.
  * fll-desktop-func:
    - revert changes made in release 0.10.18 (r16965), which were causing
      regression (unexpected file "behaviour") in persistent modus
    - note that this will again break bloated fll builds with multiple window
      managers that need to dump preseed files in the same directory
  * fll-gnome-desktop.init, fll-xfce-desktop.init:
    - do not source /usr/share/desktop-defaults-common/fll-desktop-func, no
      functions are used in initscript anymore

